Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.815
During this course, you'll use a series of tools and technology.

00:00:04.815 --> 00:00:11.070
Azure is the Cloud platform you'll use to access your virtual machine for labs.

00:00:11.070 --> 00:00:17.265
HashCat is a password cracking tool that you'll use to launch a password attack.

00:00:17.265 --> 00:00:21.885
You'll also use Windows CMD to run commands in HashCat.

00:00:21.885 --> 00:00:25.365
Nessus is a vulnerability scanning application

00:00:25.365 --> 00:00:28.155
that you'll leverage to find vulnerabilities.

00:00:28.155 --> 00:00:32.970
Finally, you'll leverage PowerPoint to present your findings,

00:00:32.970 --> 00:00:36.790
your recommended remediation strategy, and more.

